	)
	(text_box "_______________________________________________________________\n				 USER EXTERNAL INTERFACES\n* Pulldown switch to start the temp. meansurement.\n* standard SWIO for programming/debug the microcontroler.\n* Input voltage: 5V. (WARNING, NEVER USE THIS INPUT AND USB-C TOGETHER. AVOID ACCIDENTS!)"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
